First, Install the App engine SDK
    
    http://code.google.com/appengine/downloads.html#Google_App_Engine_SDK_for_Python
    
Mac: Download the DMG, put the sdk into "Applications" and run it
    
Download Source
---------------

    git clone http://github.com/justinlilly/permachart.git


Mac
-----

Open GoogleAppEngineLauncher
    Add app.yaml to SDK
    Run App
    Click "Browse"
    
Build a test graph
    http://localhost:<port>/tmp-data/

Making/Editing charts locally may fail with a known google login bug on a mac.. or maybe not.

    
Testing oEmbed
--------------
run the appengine test server

change the port on line 126 of jquery.oembed.js to match your port.

Put a test url (http://localhost:<port>/<chartkey>/) into the <a href="" on test_oembed.html

open oembedtest/test_oembed.html in your browser